title: Rollins, Richards featured guests at jazz foundation benefit
text: > Entertainment Rollins, Richards featured guests at jazz foundation benefit FILE - In this July 15, 2015, file photo, Keith Richards of the Rolling Stones performs at Le Festival d'ete de Quebec in Quebec City.Richards has saluted vocalist Merry Clayton of “Gimme Shelter” fame and an all-star gathering of jazz musicians has paid tribute to saxophonist Sonny Rollins on the Apollo Theater’s stage. It was a showcase for friends stepping up on behalf of honored and absent guests. (Photo by Barry Brecheisen/Invision/AP, File)
